# UI Component Workflow

- Inspect `packages/ui/src/components/button` before changing shared components.
- Use function declarations for React components.
- Keep actual component directory ownership separate from Storybook grouping.
- When moving a public component, update:
  - source directory
  - relative imports
  - `packages/ui/package.json` exports
  - app imports
  - Storybook title
- Avoid unnecessary explanatory copy in variants stories.
- For Storybook/Figma-based UI changes, verify rendering when possible.
- Prefer this focused check:
  `pnpm exec tsc -p packages/ui/tsconfig.json --noEmit --pretty false`
